是的，我听说了。

173
00:20:07,915 --> 00:20:09,667
Heard you were broken in.
听说有人破门而入。

174
00:20:10,668 --> 00:20:12,253
Heard you were broken in rough.
听说你伤得很重。

175
00:20:13,421 --> 00:20:17,174
And he got what he deserved.
I gave it to him.
他罪有应得。
我给了他。

176
00:20:18,467 --> 00:20:19,552
How?
如何?

177
00:20:20,803 --> 00:20:21,929
Hounds.
猎犬。

178
00:20:25,850 --> 00:20:27,685
You've changed, little bird.
你变了，小鸟。

179
00:20:34,191 --> 00:20:37,236
None of it would have happened
if you'd left king's landing with me.
这一切都不会发生
如果你和我一起离开君临。

180
00:20:37,319 --> 00:20:40,281
No littlefinger, no ramsay...
没有小指头，没有拉姆齐……

181
00:20:41,866 --> 00:20:43,200
None of it.
都没有。

182
00:20:51,542 --> 00:20:54,253
Without littlefinger,
and ramsay and the rest,
没有littlefinger,
还有拉姆齐和其他人，

183
00:20:54,336 --> 00:20:56,756
I would have stayed
a little bird all my life.
我会留下来
我一辈子都是一只小鸟。

184
00:21:18,235 --> 00:21:19,904
Man 1: Hey!
Man 2: Pour another one.
男1：嘿！
男2：再倒一杯。

185
00:21:24,158 --> 00:21:25,409
Man 3: Hey!
男3：嘿！

186
00:21:33,334 --> 00:21:34,335
Don't shoot.
不要开枪。

187
00:21:38,380 --> 00:21:40,883
It's nighttime, it's freezing,
and everyone's celebrating.
现在是晚上，很冷，
每个人都在庆祝。

188
00:21:40,966 --> 00:21:42,510
You should be celebrating with them.
你应该和他们一起庆祝。

189
00:21:43,469 --> 00:21:44,845
I am celebrating.
我在庆祝。

190
00:21:46,597 --> 00:21:48,224
Yeah, I am, too.
是的，我也是。

191
00:21:50,976 --> 00:21:53,145
I'm not gendry rivers anymore.
我不再是詹德里·里弗斯了。

192
00:21:53,229 --> 00:21:56,315
I'm gendry Baratheon,
lord of storm's end.
我是詹德利·拜拉席恩
风息堡领主。

193
00:21:57,149 --> 00:21:58,359
By order of the queen.
这是女王的命令。

194
00:22:00,528 --> 00:22:01,654
Congratulations.
祝贺你。

195
00:22:05,282 --> 00:22:07,034
I don't know how to be
lord of anything.
我不知道该怎么做
主宰一切。

196
00:22:07,117 --> 00:22:08,661
I hardly know how to use a fork.
我几乎不知道怎么用叉子。

197
00:22:08,744 --> 00:22:11,872
All I know is that you're beautiful,
and I love you,
我只知道你很美，
我爱你

198
00:22:11,956 --> 00:22:14,959
and none of it will be worth anything
if you're not with me.
这一切都将一文不值
如果你不和我在一起。

199
00:22:16,335 --> 00:22:17,419
So be with me.
所以和我在一起吧。

200
00:22:22,258 --> 00:22:25,344
Be my wife.
Be the lady of storm's end.
做我的妻子。
做风暴尽头的淑女。

201
00:22:47,616 --> 00:22:49,201
You'll be a wonderful lord,
你会是个很棒的领主

202
00:22:50,369 --> 00:22:53,163
and any lady
would be lucky to have you.
任何一位女士
有你在真是太幸运了。

203
00:22:54,498 --> 00:22:56,000
But I'm not a lady.
但我不是淑女。

204
00:22:57,376 --> 00:22:58,794
I never have been.
我从来没有去过。

205
00:23:01,046 --> 00:23:02,256
That's not me.
那不是我。

206
00:23:28,240 --> 00:23:29,658
You didn't drink.
你没有喝酒。

207
00:23:32,536 --> 00:23:34,288
- I didn't drink?
- In the game.
-我没喝酒？
-在游戏中。

208
00:23:35,873 --> 00:23:38,834
- I drank.
- In the game. This is dornish.
-我喝酒了。
-在游戏中。这是学院式的。

209
00:23:41,795 --> 00:23:45,215
This is not the game.
This is only drinking.
这不是游戏。
这只是喝酒而已。

210
00:23:46,216 --> 00:23:47,343
Suit yourself.
随便你。

211
00:23:58,270 --> 00:24:00,272
Well, you keep it warm enough in here.
好吧，你在这里保持足够的温暖。

212
00:24:04,151 --> 00:24:06,445
It's the first thing I learnt
when I came to the north.
这是我学到的第一件事
当我来到北方

213
00:24:07,112 --> 00:24:08,447
Keep your fire going.
让你的火继续燃烧。

214
00:24:09,198 --> 00:24:11,078
Every time you leave the room,
put more wood on.
每次你离开房间
再加些木头。

215
00:24:11,116 --> 00:24:13,744
Well, that's very diligent.
Very responsible.
嗯，那很勤奋。
非常负责任的。

216
00:24:13,827 --> 00:24:15,621
- Piss off.
- You know the first thing
-滚开。
-你知道第一件事

217
00:24:15,704 --> 00:24:16,830
I learned in the north?
我在北方学到的？

218
00:24:17,623 --> 00:24:19,667
I hate the fucking north.
我讨厌他妈的北方。

219
00:24:20,751 --> 00:24:22,169
It grows on you.
你会喜欢它的。

220
00:24:23,837 --> 00:24:26,340
I don't want things growing on me.
我不想让东西长在我身上。

221
00:24:27,633 --> 00:24:29,927
How about tormund giantsbane?
托蒙德巨人贝恩怎么样？

222
00:24:31,011 --> 00:24:32,554
Has he grown on you?
你越来越喜欢他了吗？

223
00:24:34,264 --> 00:24:36,016
He was very sad when you left.
你走的时候他很伤心。

224
00:24:37,726 --> 00:24:39,561
You sound quite jealous.
你听起来很嫉妒。

225
00:24:42,231 --> 00:24:43,232
I do, dontl?
我知道，不是吗？

226
00:24:48,904 --> 00:24:50,572
It's bloody hot in here.
这里太热了。

227
00:25:00,457 --> 00:25:01,959
Oh, move aside.
哦，靠边站。

228
00:25:07,589 --> 00:25:08,674
What are you doing?
你在干什么？

229
00:25:09,591 --> 00:25:10,884
I'm taking your shirt off.
我要把你的衬衫脱了。

230
00:25:58,057 --> 00:26:00,267
I've never slept with a knight before.
我从没跟骑士上过床。

231
00:26:01,602 --> 00:26:04,104
I've never slept with anyone before.
我以前从没跟人睡过。

232
00:26:06,106 --> 00:26:08,859
Then you have to drink.
Those are the rules.
然后你就得喝酒。
这是规则。

233
00:26:09,860 --> 00:26:10,986
I told you...
我告诉过你……

234
00:26:26,668 --> 00:26:27,711
Are you drunk?
你喝醉了吗？

235
00:26:38,639 --> 00:26:39,681
Only a little.
只会一点点。

236
00:26:50,442 --> 00:26:52,111
I didn't know ser jorah well...
我不太了解乔拉爵士……

237
00:26:53,320 --> 00:26:54,696
But I know this.
但我知道。

238
00:26:56,615 --> 00:26:59,910
If he could have chosen a way to die,
it would have been protecting you.
如果他可以选择一种死法，
那是在保护你。

239
00:27:01,578 --> 00:27:02,663
He loved me.
他爱我。

240
00:27:05,624 --> 00:27:07,126
And I couldn't love him back.
而我却无法爱他。

241
00:27:09,753 --> 00:27:11,171
Not the way he wanted.
不是他想要的方式。

242
00:27:14,925 --> 00:27:16,593
Not the way I love you.
不是我爱你的方式。

243
00:27:19,680 --> 00:27:20,889
Is that all right?
这样可以吗？

244
00:28:00,387 --> 00:28:02,764
I wish you'd never told me.
我真希望你没告诉我。

245
00:28:03,765 --> 00:28:05,809
If I didn't know,
I'd be happy right now.
如果我不知道，
我现在就很高兴。

246
00:28:07,978 --> 00:28:09,396
I try to forget.
我试着忘记。

247
00:28:10,939 --> 00:28:12,357
Tonight I did for a while,
今晚我做了一会儿，

248
00:28:12,441 --> 00:28:15,152
and then I saw them
gathered around you.
然后我看到了他们
聚集在你身边。

249
00:28:16,528 --> 00:28:18,405
I saw the way they looked at you.
我看到他们看你的眼神了。

250
00:28:20,032 --> 00:28:21,450
I know that look.
我知道你的表情。

251
00:28:23,243 --> 00:28:26,079
So many people have looked at me
that way, but never here.
很多人都看过我
那样做，但在这里不行。

252
00:28:26,747 --> 00:28:28,582
Never on this side of the sea.
从来没有在海的这一边。

253
00:28:29,917 --> 00:28:31,043
I told you I don't want it.
我告诉过你我不想要。

254
00:28:31,126 --> 00:28:32,920
It doesn't matter what you want.
你想要什么并不重要。

255
00:28:33,962 --> 00:28:36,215
You didn't want to be
king in the north.
你不想成为
北境之王。

256
00:28:36,298 --> 00:28:38,109
What happens when they demand
you press your claim,
当他们提出要求时会发生什么
你坚持你的要求

257
00:28:38,133 --> 00:28:39,801
and take what is mine?
拿走属于我的东西？

258
00:28:43,180 --> 00:28:44,514
I'll refuse.
我会拒绝。

259
00:28:45,307 --> 00:28:47,726
You are my queen.
I don't know what else I can say.
你是我的女王。
我不知道还能说什么。

260
00:28:47,809 --> 00:28:49,895
You can say nothing.
你什么也不能说。

261
00:28:49,978 --> 00:28:51,605
To anyone, ever.
给任何人，永远。

262
00:28:51,688 --> 00:28:53,357
Never tell them who you really are.
永远不要告诉他们你的真实身份。

263
00:28:53,941 --> 00:28:56,026
Swear your brother
and samwell tarly to secrecy,
发誓你的兄弟
山姆威尔早早地去保密，

264
00:28:56,109 --> 00:28:57,611
and tell no one else.
别告诉别人。

265
00:28:57,694 --> 00:29:00,739
Or it will take on a life of its own
and you won't be able to control it
否则它就会自生自灭
你将无法控制它

266
00:29:00,822 --> 00:29:02,241
or what it does to people.
或者它对人的影响。

267
00:29:02,324 --> 00:29:04,785
No matter how many times
you bend the knee,
无论多少次
你屈膝，

268
00:29:04,868 --> 00:29:06,828
no matter what you swear.
无论你发誓什么。

269
00:29:12,125 --> 00:29:14,962
I want it to be the way it was
between us.
我希望一切都能回到从前
我们之间。

270
00:29:24,721 --> 00:29:26,640
I have to tell sansa and Arya.
我得告诉珊莎和艾莉亚。

271
00:29:27,349 --> 00:29:32,896
Sansa will want to see me gone
and you on the iron throne.
珊莎会希望我离开
而你坐在铁王座上。

272
00:29:32,980 --> 00:29:34,064
She won't.
她不会。

273
00:29:35,023 --> 00:29:36,984
She's not the girl you grew up with.
她不是和你一起长大的女孩了。

274
00:29:37,859 --> 00:29:39,695
Not after what she's seen,
在她看到这些之后

275
00:29:40,404 --> 00:29:42,239
not after what they've done to her.
在他们对她做了那些事之后。

276
00:29:46,243 --> 00:29:47,536
I owe them the truth.
我欠他们真相。

277
00:29:48,453 --> 00:29:51,039
Even if the truth destroys us?
即使真相毁灭了我们？

278
00:29:51,123 --> 00:29:52,874
- It won't.
- It will.
-不会的。
-会的。

279
00:29:55,460 --> 00:29:57,212
I've never begged for anything...
我从来没有乞求过什么……

280
00:29:58,422 --> 00:29:59,798
But I'm begging you.
但我求你了。

281
00:30:00,882 --> 00:30:03,719
Don't do this. Please.
不要这样做。请。

282
00:30:10,309 --> 00:30:11,935
You are my queen.
你是我的女王。

283
00:30:13,312 --> 00:30:15,105
Nothing will change that.
没有什么能改变这一点。

284
00:30:18,066 --> 00:30:19,776
And they are my family.
他们是我的家人。

285
00:30:21,737 --> 00:30:23,363
We can live together.
我们可以住在一起。

286
00:30:29,286 --> 00:30:30,495
We can.
我们可以。

287
00:30:32,456 --> 00:30:34,207
I've just told you how.
我已经告诉你怎么做了。

288
00:31:10,327 --> 00:31:11,620
Half are gone.
一半都不见了。

289
00:31:15,916 --> 00:31:16,958
The northmen as well.
还有北方人。

290
00:31:24,091 --> 00:31:27,427
And the golden company
has arrived in king's landing,
还有黄金公司
已抵达君临

291
00:31:27,511 --> 00:31:29,304
courtesy of the greyjoy eret.
这是葛雷乔伊家的鸟。

292
00:31:29,388 --> 00:31:32,516
The balance has grown
distressingly even.
平衡在增长
甚至得吓人。

293
00:31:33,225 --> 00:31:35,435
When the people find out
what we have done for them,
当人们发现时
我们为他们所做的一切

294
00:31:36,311 --> 00:31:37,396
that we saved them...
我们救了他们……

295
00:31:37,479 --> 00:31:39,481
Cersei will make sure
they don't believe it.
瑟曦会确保的
他们不相信。

296
00:31:41,608 --> 00:31:42,818
We will hit her hard.
我们会狠狠地揍她。

297
00:31:43,402 --> 00:31:45,487
We will rip her out root and stem.
我们要把她连根拔起。

298
00:31:47,072 --> 00:31:49,616
The objective here is to remove Cersei
我们的目标是除掉瑟曦

299
00:31:49,699 --> 00:31:51,701
without destroying king's landing.
不破坏君临城。

300
00:31:55,664 --> 00:31:58,875
Varys: Thankfully,
she is losing allies by the day.
不同:谢天谢地,
她每天都在失去盟友。

301
00:31:59,459 --> 00:32:03,630
Yara greyjoy has retaken
the iron islands in her queen's name.
亚拉·葛雷乔伊夺回了
她女王名下的铁群岛。

302
00:32:03,713 --> 00:32:06,466
The new prince of dorne
pledges his support.
多恩的新王子
承诺支持。

303
00:32:06,550 --> 00:32:08,760
No matter how many lords
turn against her,
不管有多少领主
背叛她，

304
00:32:08,844 --> 00:32:10,387
as long as she sits
on the iron throne,
只要她坐着
在铁王座上

305
00:32:10,470 --> 00:32:13,223
she can call herself
queen of the seven kingdoms.
她可以叫自己
七大王国的女王。

306
00:32:15,475 --> 00:32:16,518
We need the capital.
我们需要资金。

307
00:32:17,727 --> 00:32:19,354
I watched the people
of king's landing
我看着人们
君临城

308
00:32:19,438 --> 00:32:21,398
rebel against their king
when they were hungry,
反抗他们的国王
当他们饿的时候，

309
00:32:21,481 --> 00:32:23,483
and that was before winter began.
那是在冬天开始之前。

310
00:32:23,942 --> 00:32:27,279
Give them the opportunity
and they will cast Cersei aside.
给他们机会
他们会抛弃瑟曦

311
00:32:29,114 --> 00:32:30,782
Jon: We'll surround the city.
乔恩：我们将包围这座城市。

312
00:32:31,783 --> 00:32:33,785
If the iron fleet
tries to ferry in more food,
如果铁舰队
试图运送更多的食物，

313
00:32:33,869 --> 00:32:35,495
the dragons will destroy them.
龙会毁灭他们。

314
00:32:36,288 --> 00:32:38,540
If the lannisters
and the golden company attack,
如果兰尼斯特家
和黄金公司的进攻，

315
00:32:38,623 --> 00:32:40,208
we'll defeat them in the field.
我们会在战场上打败他们。

316
00:32:40,292 --> 00:32:43,128
Once the people see
that Cersei is our only enemy,
一旦人们看到
瑟曦是我们唯一的敌人

317
00:32:44,004 --> 00:32:45,422
her reign is over.
她的统治结束了。

318
00:32:51,136 --> 00:32:52,220
All right.
好吧。

319
00:32:52,888 --> 00:32:54,973
Sansa: The men we have left
are exhausted.
珊莎：我们剩下的人
是筋疲力尽了。

320
00:32:55,974 --> 00:32:57,434
Many of them are wounded.
他们中的许多人受伤了。

321
00:32:57,517 --> 00:33:00,604
They'll fight better if they have
time to rest and recuperate.
如果有，他们会打得更好
是时候休息和恢复了。

322
00:33:01,897 --> 00:33:03,106
How long do you suggest?
你建议多长时间？

323
00:33:04,691 --> 00:33:07,694
I can't say for certain,
not without talking to the officers.
我不能肯定，
除非和警官们谈过。

324
00:33:11,281 --> 00:33:14,034
I came north to fight alongside you
我北上与你并肩作战

325
00:33:14,117 --> 00:33:16,745
at great cost to my armies and myself.
我和我的军队都付出了巨大的代价。

326
00:33:17,996 --> 00:33:22,209
Now that the time has come
to reciprocate, you want to postpone.
现在是时候了
作为回报，你想推迟。

327
00:33:22,709 --> 00:33:25,212
It's not just our people. It's yours.
不仅仅是我们的人民。这是你的。

328
00:33:26,171 --> 00:33:29,049
You want to throw them into a war
they're not ready to fight?
你想让他们卷入战争
他们还没准备好战斗吗？

329
00:33:29,132 --> 00:33:32,344
The longer I leave my enemies alone,
the stronger they become.
我离开我的敌人越久，
他们变得越强大。

330
00:33:36,014 --> 00:33:38,892
The northern forces
will honor their promises
北方军队
会兑现他们的承诺

331
00:33:39,559 --> 00:33:43,313
and their allegiance
to the queen of the seven kingdoms.
他们的忠诚
敬七国之女王。

332
00:33:48,860 --> 00:33:50,570
What you command, we will obey.
你的命令，我们都服从。

333
00:33:55,325 --> 00:33:56,368
Tyrion: So...
泰瑞欧:所以…

334
00:33:57,077 --> 00:33:59,287
If all are in agreement...
如果大家都同意……

335
00:34:00,372 --> 00:34:03,166
Jon and ser davos
will ride down the kingsroad
琼恩和戴佛斯爵士
会骑上国王大道吗

336
00:34:03,250 --> 00:34:04,292
with the northern troops
和北方军队一起

337
00:34:04,376 --> 00:34:07,087
and the bulk of the remaining
Dothraki and unsullied.
剩下的大部分
多斯拉克人，无垢者。

338
00:34:07,170 --> 00:34:10,048
A smaller group of us
will ride to white harbor,
我们中的一小部分人
将骑到白色的港湾，

339
00:34:10,131 --> 00:34:11,550
and sail from there to dragonstone
然后从那里坐船去龙石岛

340
00:34:11,633 --> 00:34:15,220
with our queen and her dragons
accompanying us from above.
我们的女王和她的龙
从上面陪伴我们。

341
00:34:15,303 --> 00:34:20,267
