I'd feel much better about the future
if I left here today
我对未来的感觉会好很多
如果我今天离开这里

507
00:44:29,250 --> 00:44:31,210
believing that you and Daenerys
were allies.
相信你和丹妮莉丝
是盟友。

508
00:44:31,294 --> 00:44:34,922
What are you worried about?
Jon's taking our army with him.
你在担心什么？
琼恩带着我们的军队一起走。

509
00:44:35,006 --> 00:44:37,800
- Your queen still has her dragons...
- She's your queen, too.
-你的女王还有她的龙…
-她也是你的女王

510
00:44:44,932 --> 00:44:46,684
You don't have to be her friend.
你没必要做她的朋友。

511
00:44:47,226 --> 00:44:48,644
But why provoke her?
但是为什么要激怒她呢？

512
00:44:49,562 --> 00:44:51,480
How is that in the best interest
of your family,
这怎么可能是最佳利益呢
你的家人，

513
00:44:51,564 --> 00:44:53,566
- or the north, or...?
- You're afraid of her.
-还是北方，还是…？
-你怕她。

514
00:44:56,527 --> 00:45:00,281
Every good ruler
needs to inspire a bit of fear.
每一个好的统治者
需要激发一点恐惧。

515
00:45:03,409 --> 00:45:05,786
I don't want Jon to go down there.
我不想让乔恩去那里。

516
00:45:05,870 --> 00:45:08,748
The men in my family
don't do well in the capital.
我家里的男人
不要在首都做得很好。

517
00:45:09,582 --> 00:45:13,085
No, but as your brother once told me,
he's not a stark.
不，但正如你哥哥曾经告诉我的，
他不是史塔克家的人。

518
00:45:19,258 --> 00:45:20,509
Are you all right?
你还好吗？

519
00:45:27,225 --> 00:45:29,810
Her people love her, you've seen that.
她的人民爱她，你也看到了。

520
00:45:29,894 --> 00:45:32,230
You've seen how they fight for her.
你也看到他们是怎么为她而战的。

521
00:45:32,313 --> 00:45:35,650
She wants to make the world
a better place.
她想创造世界
一个更好的地方。

522
00:45:37,652 --> 00:45:39,070
I believe in her.
我相信她。

523
00:45:54,543 --> 00:45:55,628
Tyrion.
泰瑞欧。

524
00:45:58,881 --> 00:46:01,384
What if there's someone else?
如果有别人呢？

525
00:46:01,467 --> 00:46:02,677
Someone better?
人更好?

526
00:46:11,519 --> 00:46:13,479
You're not gonna
ride the dragon south?
你不会
骑龙南下？

527
00:46:17,108 --> 00:46:18,317
Jon: Just a horse.
乔恩：只是一匹马。

528
00:46:19,652 --> 00:46:20,945
Rhaegal needs to heal.
雷加尔需要疗伤。

529
00:46:21,028 --> 00:46:23,072
He doesn't need me weighing him down.
他不需要我拖累他。

530
00:46:23,739 --> 00:46:25,992
You weigh as much
as two eras fucking.
你的体重
就像两个时代一样。

531
00:46:27,368 --> 00:46:29,203
I'm taking the free folk home.
我要把自由人带回家。

532
00:46:29,829 --> 00:46:32,123
We've had enough of the south.
我们受够了南方。

533
00:46:33,082 --> 00:46:34,875
The women down here don't like me.
这里的女人不喜欢我。

534
00:46:37,003 --> 00:46:38,754
This is the north, you know.
你知道，这是北方。

535
00:46:40,506 --> 00:46:42,758
And the free folk are welcome to stay.
我们欢迎自由民们留下来。

536
00:46:44,176 --> 00:46:45,386
It isn't home.
这里不是家。

537
00:46:46,178 --> 00:46:47,680
We need room to wander.
我们需要漫游的空间。

538
00:46:48,389 --> 00:46:49,949
I'll take them back
through castle black
我把它们拿回去
穿过黑城堡

539
00:46:49,974 --> 00:46:51,767
as soon as the winter storms pass.
只要冬天的风暴过去。

540
00:46:52,435 --> 00:46:53,853
Back where we belong.
回到属于我们的地方。

541
00:46:58,107 --> 00:46:59,817
It's where he belongs, too.
他也属于这里。

542
00:47:00,484 --> 00:47:02,570
A dire wolf has no place in the south.
可怕的狼在南方没有立足之地。

543
00:47:04,530 --> 00:47:05,740
Will you take him with you?
你会带他一起去吗？

544
00:47:07,992 --> 00:47:09,410
He'll be happier up there.
他在那里会更快乐。

545
00:47:10,953 --> 00:47:12,288
So would you.
你也会的。

546
00:47:14,373 --> 00:47:16,125
I wish I was going with you.
真希望我能和你一起去。

547
00:47:21,047 --> 00:47:22,298
This is farewell, then.
那么，这就是告别了。

548
00:47:24,050 --> 00:47:25,301
You never know.
谁知道呢。

549
00:47:31,932 --> 00:47:34,018
You've got the north in you.
你身上有北方的气息。

550
00:47:35,686 --> 00:47:36,979
The real north.
真正的北方。

551
00:48:09,637 --> 00:48:12,640
Yes, we”, um,
the nights have been getting longer
是的，我们……
夜晚越来越长了

552
00:48:12,723 --> 00:48:15,851
and there wasn't that much
to do in oldtown.
其实并没有那么多
在老城区做的事。

553
00:48:15,935 --> 00:48:18,104
There's only so many books
a person can read, so we...
只有这么多书
一个人可以阅读，所以我们…

554
00:48:18,187 --> 00:48:20,940
I'm sure he knows how it happens, Sam.
我相信他知道这是怎么回事，萨姆。

555
00:48:24,318 --> 00:48:26,737
If it's a boy,
we want to name him "Jon."
如果是个男孩，
我们想给他起名叫“乔恩”。

556
00:48:30,116 --> 00:48:31,534
I hope it's a girl.
我希望是个女孩。

557
00:48:50,594 --> 00:48:52,555
You're the best friend I ever had.
你是我最好的朋友。

558
00:48:55,057 --> 00:48:56,267
You too, Sam.
你也是，萨姆。

559
00:49:57,828 --> 00:49:59,914
Tyrion: Think of the past 20 years.
提利昂：想想过去的20年。

560
00:50:00,873 --> 00:50:03,375
The war, the murder, the misery.
战争，谋杀，苦难。

561
00:50:03,959 --> 00:50:06,337
All of it because Robert Baratheon
loved someone
都是因为劳勃·拜拉席恩
爱的人

562
00:50:06,420 --> 00:50:08,297
who didn't love him back.
没有爱他的人。

563
00:50:10,424 --> 00:50:11,592
How many others know?
还有多少人知道？

564
00:50:13,427 --> 00:50:16,138
Including us? Eight.
包括我们?八个。

565
00:50:16,222 --> 00:50:18,182
Well, then it's not a secret anymore.
那就不再是秘密了。

566
00:50:18,265 --> 00:50:19,683
It's information.
它的信息。

567
00:50:20,351 --> 00:50:23,479
If a handful of people know now,
hundreds will know soon.
如果现在有一小部分人知道了，
数百人很快就会知道。

568
00:50:23,562 --> 00:50:24,855
Then what happens?
然后会发生什么？

569
00:50:24,939 --> 00:50:26,690
She loses the north.
她失去了北方。

570
00:50:26,774 --> 00:50:29,485
She loses the vale,
sansa will make sure of that.
她失去了价值，
珊莎会确保这一点。

571
00:50:29,568 --> 00:50:31,111
No, it's worse than that.
不，比那还糟。

572
00:50:31,195 --> 00:50:32,780
He has the better claim to the throne.
他更有资格继承王位。

573
00:50:33,906 --> 00:50:35,699
He doesn't want the throne.
他不想要王位。

574
00:50:36,242 --> 00:50:38,244
I'm not sure it matters what he wants.
我觉得他想要什么不重要。

575
00:50:39,912 --> 00:50:42,748
The fact is, people are drawn to him.
事实是，人们都被他吸引了。

576
00:50:43,332 --> 00:50:44,833
Wildlings, northmen.
野人,北方人。

577
00:50:46,835 --> 00:50:48,170
He's a war hero.
他是个战争英雄。

578
00:50:52,633 --> 00:50:54,051
He loves our queen.
他爱我们的女王。

579
00:50:56,303 --> 00:50:57,555
And she loves him.
她爱他。

580
00:50:59,974 --> 00:51:02,434
If we marry them,
they could rule together.
如果我们和他们结婚，
他们可以一起统治。

581
00:51:03,227 --> 00:51:04,562
She's his aunt.
她是他的姨妈。

582
00:51:04,645 --> 00:51:06,039
That never stopped a Targaryen before.
坦格利安家族的人从来没被这招吓过。

583
00:51:06,063 --> 00:51:07,731
No, but Jon grew up in winterfell.
没有，但琼恩是在临冬城长大的。

584
00:51:07,815 --> 00:51:09,900
Is marrying your aunt
common in the north?
就是娶你的姨妈
在北方很常见吗？

585
00:51:12,820 --> 00:51:14,363
You know our queen better than I do.
你比我更了解我们的女王。

586
00:51:14,446 --> 00:51:16,126
Do you think
she wants to share the throne?
你认为
她想分享王位？

587
00:51:17,700 --> 00:51:20,035
She does not like to have
her authority questioned.
她不喜欢有
她的权威受到质疑。

588
00:51:20,119 --> 00:51:22,788
Something she has in common
with every monarch who ever lived.
她有一些共同点
和每一位君主在一起。

589
00:51:24,123 --> 00:51:25,708
I worry about her state of mind.
我担心她的精神状态。

590
00:51:26,125 --> 00:51:27,960
We are advisors to the queen.
我们是女王的顾问。

591
00:51:28,043 --> 00:51:31,255
Worrying about her state of mind
is ourjob.
担心她的精神状态
ourjob。

592
00:51:39,346 --> 00:51:41,432
We still have to take king's landing.
我们还得拿下君临。

593
00:51:42,558 --> 00:51:44,643
Maybe Cersei will win and kill us all.
也许瑟曦会赢，把我们都杀了。

594
00:51:45,227 --> 00:51:46,854
That would solve our problems.
这样我们的问题就解决了。

595
00:53:51,019 --> 00:53:53,439
Get to the skiff. Now!
到小船那里去。现在!

596
00:53:55,524 --> 00:53:56,567
Soldier 1: Spears!
士兵1：长矛！

597
00:53:56,650 --> 00:53:58,569
Soldier 2: They're coming round again!
士兵2：他们又回来了！

598
00:54:07,953 --> 00:54:09,121
Soldier 3: Go!
士兵3：快走！

599
00:54:09,204 --> 00:54:10,456
Soldier 4: Clear!
士兵4：安全！

600
00:54:13,041 --> 00:54:14,126
Woman: No!
女人:不!

601
00:54:32,478 --> 00:54:33,758
Soldier 4: Go! Soldier 5: Clear!
士兵4：快走！士兵5：安全！

602
00:55:10,265 --> 00:55:11,475
Missandei?
Missandei吗?

603
00:55:12,935 --> 00:55:14,353
Missandei!
Missandei !

604
00:55:20,234 --> 00:55:21,735
Missandei!
Missandei !

605
00:55:27,032 --> 00:55:28,826
Cersei: Our message
was well-received, then?
瑟曦：我们的信息
很受欢迎吧？

606
00:55:28,909 --> 00:55:32,120
Qyburn: Your people have heard
the usurper is coming.
你的人听说了
篡位者来了。

607
00:55:32,204 --> 00:55:37,084
They are grateful for your protection
within the walls of the red keep.
他们感激你的保护
在红堡的城墙内。

608
00:55:39,336 --> 00:55:40,754
You're certain about the dragon?
你确定是龙吗？

609
00:55:41,547 --> 00:55:43,632
I saw it sink beneath the waves.
我看见它沉到海浪下面。

610
00:55:44,049 --> 00:55:45,801
That must have been glorious.
那一定很光荣。

611
00:55:48,178 --> 00:55:50,389
The glory is yours, my queen.
荣耀属于你，我的女王。

612
00:55:51,849 --> 00:55:54,142
When the war is won,
the lion shall rule the land,
当战争胜利时
狮子将统治大地，

613
00:55:54,226 --> 00:55:55,978
the kraken shall rule the sea...
海怪将统治大海……

614
00:55:57,563 --> 00:56:00,566
And our child
shall one day rule them all.
还有我们的孩子
总有一天会统治他们。

615
00:56:17,499 --> 00:56:19,084
She's coming for you.
她来找你了。

616
00:56:20,252 --> 00:56:21,461
Of course she is.
她当然是。

617
00:56:24,381 --> 00:56:25,924
Keep the gates open.
保持大门敞开。

618
00:56:26,592 --> 00:56:28,653
If she wants to take the castle,
she'll have to murder
如果她想拿下城堡，
她将不得不杀人

619
00:56:28,677 --> 00:56:30,888
thousands of innocent people first.
首先是成千上万无辜的人。

620
00:56:37,436 --> 00:56:39,438
So much for the "breaker of chains."
这就是所谓的“打破锁链的人”。

621
00:56:53,535 --> 00:56:55,829
Grey worm: We will storm the city,
my queen.
灰虫：我们将突袭这座城市，
我的女王。

622
00:56:55,913 --> 00:56:58,665
We will kill your enemies.
All of them.
我们会杀死你的敌人。
所有的。

623
00:56:59,207 --> 00:57:00,417
Varys: Your grace.
瓦里斯：陛下。

624
00:57:01,960 --> 00:57:05,756
I promised you I would look you
in the eye and speak directly
我答应过你我会看你的
直视眼睛，直接说话

625
00:57:05,839 --> 00:57:07,925
if I ever thought
you were making a mistake.
如果我曾经想过
你犯了一个错误。

626
00:57:11,511 --> 00:57:13,931
This is a mistake.
这是一个错误。

627
00:57:17,017 --> 00:57:19,353
You saw my child fall from the sky.
你看到我的孩子从天上掉下来。

628
00:57:21,021 --> 00:57:22,439
They took missandei.
他们带走了弥桑黛。

629
00:57:23,273 --> 00:57:25,233
Varys: Cersei needs to be destroyed,
瓦里斯：瑟曦必须被消灭，

630
00:57:25,317 --> 00:57:29,321
but if we attack king's landing
with drogon and the unsullied
但如果我们进攻君临
有恶龙和无垢者

631
00:57:29,404 --> 00:57:33,033
and the Dothraki, tens of thousands
of innocents will die.
多斯拉克人则有数以万计
无数无辜的人将死去。

632
00:57:33,617 --> 00:57:36,620
That is why Cersei
is bringing them into the red keep.
这就是为什么瑟曦
把他们带进红堡。

633
00:57:38,205 --> 00:57:41,083
These are the people
you came here to protect.
这些人
你是来保护我的。

634
00:57:41,959 --> 00:57:43,126
I beg you, your grace.
我求您了，陛下。

635
00:57:43,210 --> 00:57:46,546
Do not destroy the city
you came to save.
不毁灭这城吗
你是来救人的。

636
00:57:47,255 --> 00:57:50,801
Do not become what you
have always struggled to defeat.
不变成什么你
总是挣扎着去打败。

637
00:57:55,931 --> 00:57:58,016
Do you believe we're here
for a reason, lord varys?
你相信我们在这里吗
有什么原因吗，瓦里斯大人？

638
00:58:02,437 --> 00:58:05,273
I'm here to free the world
from tyrants.
我是来解放世界的
从暴君。

639
00:58:06,441 --> 00:58:08,110
That is my destiny...
这就是我的命运……

640
00:58:09,319 --> 00:58:11,947
And I will serve it,
no matter the cost.
我要端上来，
不计代价。

641
00:58:19,496 --> 00:58:21,915
It could be a fortnight
before Jon and the allied armies
可能是两周
在琼恩和联军之前

642
00:58:21,999 --> 00:58:23,208
make it to king's landing.
去君临吧。

643
00:58:24,376 --> 00:58:27,087
In the meantime,
demand Cersei's surrender.
与此同时，
要求瑟曦投降。

644
00:58:27,170 --> 00:58:30,340
Offer her her life
in exchange for the throne.
给她生命
以换取王位。

645
00:58:32,426 --> 00:58:34,469
If there's a chance
to avoid the coming slaughter,
如果有机会的话
为了避免即将到来的屠杀，

646
00:58:34,553 --> 00:58:36,304
we should make the effort.
我们应该努力。

647
00:58:37,180 --> 00:58:39,349
Speaking to Cersei
will not prevent a slaughter.
对瑟曦说
不会阻止一场屠杀。

648
00:58:42,227 --> 00:58:44,021
But perhaps it's good the people see
但也许让人们看到是好事

649
00:58:44,104 --> 00:58:47,816
that Daenerys stormborn made
every effort to avoid bloodshed,
是风暴降生丹妮莉丝做的
一切避免流血的努力，

650
00:58:47,899 --> 00:58:50,193
and Cersei Lannister refused.
瑟曦·兰尼斯特拒绝了。

651
00:58:52,362 --> 00:58:55,198
They should know whom to blame
when the sky falls down upon them.
他们应该知道该怪谁
天塌下来的时候。

652
00:59:09,796 --> 00:59:12,340
I've served tyrants most of my life.
我大半辈子都在为暴君服务。

653
00:59:13,341 --> 00:59:15,761
They all talk about destiny.
他们都在谈论命运。

654
00:59:16,887 --> 00:59:19,931
She's a girl who walked into a fire
with three stones
她是一个走进火里的女孩
用三块石头

655
00:59:20,015 --> 00:59:22,642
and walked out with three dragons.
带着三条龙走了出去。

656
00:59:22,726 --> 00:59:25,479
How could she not believe in destiny?
她怎么能不相信命运呢？

657
00:59:25,562 --> 00:59:27,564
Perhaps that's the problem.
也许这就是问题所在。

658
00:59:27,647 --> 00:59:30,650
Her life has convinced her that
she was sent here to save us all.
她的生活使她确信
她被派来拯救我们所有人。

659
00:59:30,734 --> 00:59:32,569
And how do you know she wasn't?
你怎么知道她不是？

660
00:59:34,821 --> 00:59:36,698
Then there's the problem of Jon snow.
接下来就是琼恩·雪诺的问题。

661
00:59:43,371 --> 00:59:46,083
Perhaps it's actually a solution.
也许这实际上是一个解决方案。

662
00:59:48,043 --> 00:59:49,086
You know them both.
他们两个你都认识。

663
00:59:49,169 --> 00:59:52,214
Tell me, who do you think
would make a better ruler?
告诉我，你认为是谁
会成为更好的统治者吗？

664
00:59:57,594 --> 00:59:59,434
He doesn't want the throne.
他不想要王位。

665
01:00:00,013 --> 01:00:01,932
That's why he bent the knee.
这就是他屈膝的原因。

666
01:00:02,724 --> 01:00:04,142
Have you considered the best ruler
你考虑过最好的尺子吗

667
01:00:04,226 --> 01:00:05,936
might be someone
who doesn't want to rule?
可能是某人
谁不想统治呢？

668
01:00:06,770 --> 01:00:09,022
We're discussing treason.
我们在讨论叛国罪。

669
01:00:10,148 --> 01:00:11,828
Don't pretend
you haven't thought about it.
不要假装
你还没想过呢。

670
01:00:11,858 --> 01:00:14,694
Of course I've thought about it.
Thoughts aren't treason.
我当然想过了。
思想不是叛国。

671
01:00:17,239 --> 01:00:19,658
He's temperate and measured.
他有节制，有分寸。

672
01:00:20,367 --> 01:00:23,912
He's a man, which makes him more
appealing to the lords of Westeros,
他是个男人，所以他更
向维斯特洛的领主们求助

673
01:00:23,995 --> 01:00:25,455
whose support we are going to need.
我们需要他的支持。

674
01:00:26,623 --> 01:00:28,208
Joffrey was a man.
乔佛里是个男人。

675
01:00:28,291 --> 01:00:30,252
I don't think a cock
is a true qualification,
我不认为是鸡巴
是一个真正的资格，

676
01:00:30,335 --> 01:00:31,419
as I'm sure you'd agree.
我相信你也会同意

677
01:00:31,503 --> 01:00:33,588
And he's the heir to the throne.
他是王位的继承人。

678
01:00:33,672 --> 01:00:37,467
Yes, because he's a man.
Cocks are important, I'm afraid.
是的，因为他是个男人。
恐怕鸡巴很重要。

679
01:00:40,428 --> 01:00:42,639
What about my earlier proposal?
我之前的提议怎么样？

680
01:00:43,849 --> 01:00:45,725
They could rule together
as king and queen.
他们可以一起统治
作为国王和王后。

681
01:00:47,435 --> 01:00:49,062
She's too strong for him.
她对他来说太强大了。

682
01:00:49,896 --> 01:00:53,400
She'd bend him to her will,
as she already has.
她会让他屈从于她的意志
她已经这么做了。

683
01:00:53,483 --> 01:00:56,069
He could temper her worst impulses.
他能缓和她最坏的冲动。

684
01:00:56,736 --> 01:00:57,946
As you have?
像你一样？

685
01:01:01,700 --> 01:01:03,201
You're drinking quite a lot.
你喝得太多了。

686
01:01:06,288 --> 01:01:09,207
A Targaryen father and a stark mother.
坦格利安家族的父亲和史塔克家族的母亲。

687
01:01:10,208 --> 01:01:11,751
Jon's the one man alive
琼恩是唯一活着的人

688
01:01:11,835 --> 01:01:14,880
who might actually be able to keep
the north in the seven kingdoms.
谁可能会保留
北方的七国。

689
01:01:14,963 --> 01:01:16,440
How many kings and queens
have you served?
有多少国王和王后
你服过役吗？

690
01:01:16,464 --> 01:01:17,757
Five? Six? I've lost count.
五个?六个?我数不清了。

691
01:01:17,841 --> 01:01:20,010
- You've always known my reasons.
- At a certain point,
-你一直都知道我的理由。
-在某一时刻

692
01:01:20,093 --> 01:01:22,693
you choose a person you believe in,
and you fight for that person.
你选择一个你信任的人，
你为那个人而奋斗。

693
01:01:22,721 --> 01:01:25,182
Even if you know it's a mistake?
即使你知道这是个错误？

694
01:01:27,058 --> 01:01:28,810
I believe in our queen.
我相信我们的女王。

695
01:01:31,354 --> 01:01:32,856
She'll make the right choice.
她会做出正确的选择。

696
01:01:35,317 --> 01:01:37,944
With the help of her onal advisors.
在她个人顾问的帮助下。

697
01:01:41,740 --> 01:01:44,075
You know where my onalty stands.
你知道我的立场。

698
01:01:44,159 --> 01:01:46,494
You know I will never
betray the realm.
你知道我永远不会
背叛王国。

699
01:01:46,578 --> 01:01:48,079
What is the realm?
什么是王国？

700
01:01:48,163 --> 01:01:49,998
A vast continent,
home to millions of people,
广袤的大陆，
这里是数百万人的家园

701
01:01:50,081 --> 01:01:52,209
most of whom don't care
who sits on the iron throne.
大多数人都不在乎
谁坐在铁王座上。

702
01:01:52,292 --> 01:01:54,127
Millions of people,
many of whom will die
数百万人，
他们中的许多人会死去

703
01:01:54,211 --> 01:01:56,421
if the wrong person
sits on that throne.
如果找错了人
坐在那个宝座上。

704
01:01:57,172 --> 01:02:00,133
We don't know their names,
but they're just as real as you and I.
我们不知道他们的名字，
但他们和你我一样真实

705
01:02:00,217 --> 01:02:01,509
They deserve to live.
他们应该活下去。

706
01:02:01,593 --> 01:02:03,428
They deserve food for their children.
他们应该为自己的孩子提供食物。

707
01:02:07,390 --> 01:02:11,144
I will act in their interest,
no matter the personal cost.
我会为他们的利益行事
不管付出多少个人代价。

708
01:02:13,647 --> 01:02:15,857
So, what happens to her?
那么，她后来怎么样了？

709
01:02:23,823 --> 01:02:24,824
Please.
请。

710
01:02:33,541 --> 01:02:35,669
I've spoken as honestly as I can.
我已经尽可能诚实地说了。

711
01:02:37,545 --> 01:02:39,673
Each of us has a choice to make.
我们每个人都要做出选择。

712
01:02:41,258 --> 01:02:43,260
I pray we choose wisely.
我祈祷我们能做出明智的选择。

713
01:03:00,151 --> 01:03:01,911
Man 1: All right,
I'll put another one on it.
男1：好吧，
我再放一个上去。

714
01:03:02,237 --> 01:03:03,589
Man 2: He's headed down to the cellar.
男人2：他去地窖了。

715
01:03:03,613 --> 01:03:06,825
Man 3: I'll need a cart over here.
Man 4: That's it, thanks.
男士3：我需要一辆手推车。
男4：就这样，谢谢。

716
01:03:06,908 --> 01:03:08,743
Thank you.
谢谢你！

717
01:03:18,503 --> 01:03:20,630
As are the rest of her advisors.
她的其他顾问也是。

718
01:03:23,174 --> 01:03:24,217
What happened?
发生了什么事?

719
01:03:30,056 --> 01:03:32,892
Euron greyjoy ambushed
queen Daenerys and her eret.
攸伦·葛雷乔伊中了埋伏
丹妮莉丝王后和她的女儿。

720
01:03:34,644 --> 01:03:37,397
One of the dragons was killed,
several ships destroyed,
其中一条龙被杀了
几艘船被毁，

721
01:03:37,480 --> 01:03:38,898
missandei captured.
missandei被俘。

722
01:03:41,609 --> 01:03:44,738
I always wanted to be there
when they execute your sister.
我一直想去那里
当他们处决你妹妹的时候。

723
01:03:45,864 --> 01:03:47,615
Seems like I won't get the chance.
看来我没有机会了。

724
01:04:55,183 --> 01:04:57,060
They're going to destroy that city.
他们要摧毁那座城市。

725
01:04:58,436 --> 01:04:59,938
You know they will.
你知道他们会的。

726
01:05:00,855 --> 01:05:02,607
Jaime: Have you ever
run away from a fight?
詹姆：你有没有
从一场打斗中逃跑？

727
01:05:04,401 --> 01:05:07,028
You're not like your sister.
You're not.
你不像你姐姐。
你不是。

728
01:05:07,737 --> 01:05:09,280
You're better than she is.
你比她强。

729
01:05:09,364 --> 01:05:11,866
You're a good man
and you can't save her.
你是个好人
你救不了她。

730
01:05:11,950 --> 01:05:13,785
You don't need to die with her.
你不需要和她一起死。

731
01:05:14,494 --> 01:05:15,578
Stay here.
待在这里。

732
01:05:17,330 --> 01:05:18,748
Stay with me.
别离开我。

733
01:05:20,417 --> 01:05:21,626
Please.
请。

734
01:05:23,378 --> 01:05:24,462
Stay.
留下来。

735
01:05:31,136 --> 01:05:32,762
You think I'm a good man?
你觉得我是个好人？

736
01:05:37,809 --> 01:05:41,896
I pushed a boy out a tower window,
crippled him for life
我把一个男孩推出了塔楼的窗户，
使他终生残疾

737
01:05:42,689 --> 01:05:43,773
for Cersei.
瑟曦。

738
01:05:46,818 --> 01:05:49,696
I strangled my cousin
with my own hands
我勒死了我的表弟
用我自己的双手

739
01:05:50,697 --> 01:05:52,782
just to get back to Cersei.
就为了回到瑟曦身边

740
01:05:55,785 --> 01:05:57,245
I would have murdered
我会杀了你

741
01:05:57,579 --> 01:06:00,707
every man, woman and child in riverrun
奔流城的每一个男人、女人和孩子

742
01:06:01,499 --> 01:06:02,709
for Cersei.
瑟曦。

743
01:06:11,551 --> 01:06:12,969
She's hateful.
她是可恨的。

744
01:06:15,221 --> 01:06:16,431
And so am I.
我也是。

745
01:08:51,461 --> 01:08:52,670
My lord.
我的主。

746
01:08:56,007 --> 01:08:59,052
Queen Daenerys demands
Cersei's unconditional surrender
丹妮莉丝王后要求
瑟曦无条件投降

747
01:08:59,135 --> 01:09:01,679
and the immediate release
of missandei of naath.
立即释放
乃特的弥珊黛。

748
01:09:03,514 --> 01:09:07,560
Queen Cersei demands
Daenerys's unconditional surrender.
瑟曦太后要求
丹妮莉丝无条件投降。

749
01:09:08,102 --> 01:09:11,522
If she refuses, missandei of naath
will die here and now.
如果她拒绝，纳斯的弥桑黛
会死在此时此地。

750
01:09:13,483 --> 01:09:14,567
Beurn...
Beurn……

751
01:09:15,985 --> 01:09:17,820
You're a rational man.
你是个理性的人。

752
01:09:17,904 --> 01:09:20,406
Or so I flatter myself, my lord.
至少我是这么想的，大人。

753
01:09:20,948 --> 01:09:22,367
We have a chance here,
我们还有机会

754
01:09:23,660 --> 01:09:26,579
perhaps our last chance,
to avoid carnage.
也许是我们最后的机会，
为了避免大屠杀。

755
01:09:27,205 --> 01:09:28,289
Yes.
是。

756
01:09:29,916 --> 01:09:31,000
Help me.
帮助我。

757
01:09:32,293 --> 01:09:34,379
I don't want to see this city burn.
我不想看到这座城市被烧毁。

758
01:09:35,421 --> 01:09:38,341
I don't want to hear the screams
of children burning alive.
我不想听到尖叫声
孩子们被活活烧死。

759
01:09:40,426 --> 01:09:43,304
No, it is not a pleasant sound.
不，这不是悦耳的声音。

760
01:09:45,598 --> 01:09:47,767
I... I don't want to hear it.
我…我不想听。

761
01:09:48,768 --> 01:09:50,186
Help me save this city.
帮我拯救这座城市。

762
01:09:52,313 --> 01:09:54,816
My lord, I am only a mouthpiece
for our queen.
大人，我只是个喉舌
为了我们的女王。

763
01:09:54,899 --> 01:09:56,109
Tyrion: Your queen.
提利昂：你的女王。

764
01:09:56,818 --> 01:09:58,820
Cersei is queen of the seven kingdoms.
瑟曦是七大王国的女王。

765
01:09:58,903 --> 01:10:00,029
You are her subject.
你是她的主题。

766
01:10:00,113 --> 01:10:01,739
Her reign is over.
她的统治结束了。

767
01:10:02,407 --> 01:10:04,867
You understand this.
Help her understand it.
你懂的。
帮助她理解。

768
01:10:04,951 --> 01:10:07,370
We understand nothing of the sort.
我们对此一无所知。

769
01:10:08,788 --> 01:10:11,040
Your queen's last dragon
is vulnerable.
你王后的最后一条龙
是脆弱的。

770
01:10:11,582 --> 01:10:14,293
Your armies
are battle-weary and depleted,
你的军队
疲于奔命，精疲力竭，

771
01:10:14,377 --> 01:10:17,797
while ours have been reinforced
with the golden compan...
而我们的部队已经增援了
有黄金陪伴……

772
01:10:35,106 --> 01:10:36,524
Captain: Ready!
船长:准备好了!

773
01:10:37,734 --> 01:10:38,818
Nock!
诺!

774
01:10:41,529 --> 01:10:42,780
Draw!
画!

775
01:11:49,347 --> 01:11:52,099
I know you don't care
about your people.
我知道你不在乎
关于你的人。

776
01:11:54,101 --> 01:11:55,311
Why should you?
你为什么要这么做？

777
01:11:57,355 --> 01:12:00,191
They hate you and you hate them.
他们恨你，你也恨他们。

778
01:12:06,405 --> 01:12:08,407
But you're not a monster.
但你不是怪物。

779
01:12:10,868 --> 01:12:12,078
I know this.
我知道这个。

780
01:12:14,288 --> 01:12:16,499
I know this because I've seen it.
我知道这些是因为我亲眼所见。

781
01:12:21,045 --> 01:12:23,339
You've always loved your children.
你一直很爱你的孩子。

782
01:12:25,383 --> 01:12:27,802
More than yourself...
不仅仅是你自己……

783
01:12:27,885 --> 01:12:29,262
More than Jaime...
不只是詹姆……

784
01:12:32,139 --> 01:12:33,558
More than anything.
比什么都重要。

785
01:12:36,519 --> 01:12:37,728
I beg you.
我求你了。

786
01:12:40,523 --> 01:12:43,484
If not for yourself,
then for your child.
如果不是为了你自己，
然后是你的孩子。

787
01:12:47,572 --> 01:12:48,990
Your reign is over,
你的统治结束了

788
01:12:50,157 --> 01:12:52,577
but that doesn't mean
your life has to end.
但这并不意味着
你的生命必须结束。

789
01:12:56,080 --> 01:12:58,499
It doesn't mean your baby has to die.
这并不意味着你的孩子必须死。

790
01:13:46,839 --> 01:13:49,926
If you have any last words,
now is the time.
如果你有什么遗言
现在是时候了。

791
01:14:14,992 --> 01:14:16,410
Dracarys.
Dracarys。

792
01:14:26,045 --> 01:14:27,129
No.
否。

